title: #704 - Brendan Schaub
description:
Brendan Schaub, former UFC fighter, cohost of "The Fighter and the Kid" and "The King and The Sting" podcasts and host of "Below The Belt" on Showtime, joins Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt live in studio.
